public class ObjectViewModel2\n{\n    public string PropertyA { get; private set; }\n    public string PropertyB { get; private set; }\n    public string PropertyC { get; private set; }\n\n    public void SetProperties()\n    {\n        SetPropertyA();\n        SetPropertyB();\n        SetPropertyC();\n    }\n\n    private void SetPropertyA()\n    {\n        PropertyA = GetDataFromRepository("PropertyA");\n    }\n\n    private void SetPropertyB()\n    {\n        PropertyB = GetDataFromRepository("PropertyB");\n    }\n\n    private void SetPropertyC()\n    {\n        PropertyC = GetDataFromRepository("PropertyC");\n    }\n\n    private string GetDataFromRepository(string propertyName)\n    {\n        // Simulate data retrieval\n        return $"Data for {propertyName}";\n    }\n}